## Risk Register

| Risk | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|------------|
| Firebase Google Sign-In config issues | Medium | Complete email/password auth first; Google is a bonus |
| MongoDB Atlas network access | Low | Whitelist `0.0.0.0/0` during development |
| Expo Go incompatibility | Low | Use Expo SDK 50+ which supports most plugins |
| AsyncStorage deprecation | Low | Use `@react-native-async-storage/async-storage` explicitly |

---

## Definition of Done

A feature is "done" when:
1. It works correctly in the happy path.
2. Basic error cases return meaningful HTTP status codes and messages.
3. No secrets are hardcoded.
4. The README explains how to trigger it.